n?\\\"\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At a dance studio on trendy Melrose Avenue in Los Angeles this week, Edra led a half-dozen aspiring breakers through a high-energy class.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0974599424945216e-15, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dance studio\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"trendy Melrose Avenue\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"Edra\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"a half-dozen aspiring breakers\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"a high-energy class\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need music in our lives!\\\"\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she shouted to her pupils before turning the volume way up on hip-hop trio Digable Planets' 1992 hit \\\"Rebirth of Slick (Cool Like Dat).\\\"\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her pupils\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"the volume\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"hip-hop trio\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"Digable Planets\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"Rebirth\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"Slick\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"Dat\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressed in an oversized green Gogo Squeez hoodie and loose blue Nike sweatpants, she locked into the music and was soon letting loose the head spins, flips and elite footwork that made her the Red Bull BC One World Champion in 2021.\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VI\", \"score\": 0.9999999949859557, \"rank\": 3.0463618837888358e-09, \"text\": \"Gogo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VI\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Final_Fantasy_VI\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9786342163198347, \"rank\": 0.01730604858944765, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"the head spins\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"flips\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"elite footwork\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Are you a B-Girl already?\\\"\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a B-Girl\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she asked one beaming student after she pulled off a move.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one beaming student\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are just having fun, that's all we are doing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking has been compared to boxing due to the one-on-one nature of its battles and even ring walks and also to gymnastics given the acrobatic skills involved.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"the one-on-one nature\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"its battles\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"walks\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"the acrobatic skills\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Edra said it is more closely aligned to skateboarding, which also prizes creativity and technical prowess and has rapidly become one of the most popular Olympic sports following its debut at the Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Edra\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding\", \"from\": 2037, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"technical prowess\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"the most popular Olympic sports\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"its debut\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She called breaking and skateboarding \\\"art-sports,\\\" so it is fitting then that breaking, skateboarding, BMX freestyle and 3X3 basketball will all share the La Concorde open air arena in Paris during the Games.\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2318, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.3219901466463684e-13, \"text\": \"BMX freestyle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freestyle_BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.028225313611617e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrase