, \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.3430399092578573e-12, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her ticket\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"the final Olympic qualification series\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"only a top 16 finish\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She trains twice a day with mornings focused on building skills and honing technique while evening is reserved for tapping into the creative side, connecting to the music and being in the moment.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 3017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mornings\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"building skills\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"technique\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"evening\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"the creative side\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"the music\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can be a competitive person so I still train very hard to focus on doing my best to win, but we are artist-athletes,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a competitive person\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"artist-athletes\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's still subjective to a certain extent.\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain extent\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's whoever is killing it that day.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These battles are a very fun, competitive game but it's also inspi